frames.caption: A warrior clad in golden armor kneels solemnly on ancient stone steps, surrounded by lit candles. Behind her, a grand statue of a serene, seated figure looms, framed by towering columns of a temple ruin. The scene is bathed in a soft, mystical light, enhancing the atmosphere of reverence and antiquity.
frames.description: The scene is set in an ancient temple ruin, where a lone warrior kneels in a moment of contemplation or prayer. The setting is dominated by a large statue and classical architecture, suggesting a historical or mythical context.

frames.caption: A woman in golden armor stands confidently in front of an ancient temple. Behind her, a large statue and towering columns create a majestic backdrop. The sunlight filters through the clouds, casting a dramatic glow over the scene.
frames.description: The scene is set in an ancient, mythical setting with a focus on a strong, armored woman. The architecture suggests a classical or fantasy theme, with large stone columns and a prominent statue. The atmosphere is one of awe and power, enhanced by the dramatic lighting.
